", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"an operational athletics test\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP An operational track and field test was held on Tuesday at the Stade de France, where young athletes from the host nation and abroad gathered to try out the facilities for the various athletics events that will take place at the stadium after the 2024 Summer Olympics get underway on July 26.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An operational track and field test\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"young athletes\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"the host nation\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the facilities\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"the various athletics events\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The renovation of the Stade de France for the Paris Games began in 2021, and among the new features are nearly 150 sports floodlights illuminating the arena.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The renovation\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the new features\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 150 sports floodlights\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have been replaced with energy-efficient LED technology, as well as architectural lights that will brighten the surface of the stadium's roof to create light shows.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"energy-efficient LED technology\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"architectural lights\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium's roof\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"light shows\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Giant screens the size of tennis courts \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 more than 240 square meters \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 have been installed in the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Giant screens\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis courts\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 240 square meters\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty-three athletics events, 160 para-athletics competitions and two rugby sevens games will take place at the stadium during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Forty-three athletics events\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"160 para-athletics competitions\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"two rugby sevens games\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, the track looks great.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I was flying, even though I got off to a bad start in my series,\\\" French sprinter Raphalledy Guillaume said.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8752932927132424, \"rank\": 0.1240773825909101, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bad start\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"my series\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still managed to keep going and make up more than ten seconds.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than ten seconds\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, I could not beat my PB (personal best), but it's still a great experience running here.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999989803796521, \"rank\": 1.0175106086286119e-06, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great experience\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The track allows us to take off.\\\"\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The track\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00